🍉️1.searching the in array.
  --> select * from sal_emp where pay[1]=1000 or pay[2]=30000;

🍉️2.Other query.
  --> select * from sal_emp where 12000=ANY(pay);
  --> select * from sal_emp where 1000=ALL(pay);
